<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 11. SEM of radula of Platydoris guarani. A panoramic view B central region with rachidian tooth absent C lateral teeth. Scale bars: 300 µm (A); 100 µm (B); 30 µm (C)." , "Figure 7. Platydoris guarani, living animals. A. Dorsal view, specimen from Papagaio, Cabo Frio, Rio de Janeiro (MZSP 97331). B. Same, ventral view. C. Living animal with spawning, specimen from Enseada da Meia Lua, Cabo Frio, Rio de Janeiro (MZSP 97625). All photograph by V. Padula." , "Figure 8. Platydoris guarani. A circulatory and excretory system, ventral view B renal vesicle C medium digestive system, dorsal view D detail of salivar glands. Scale bars: 2 mm (A, B, D); 5 mm (C)." , "Figure 9. Platydoris guarani. Odontophore. A dorsal view with radula B same, ventral view C same, dorsal view with removed radula D same, dorsal view, with folded down muscles. Scale bars: 2 mm." , "Figure 10. Platydoris guarani. Reproductive system A general ventral view B detail of Bursa copulatrix, seminal receptacle, uterine duct and vagina. Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/177383" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/177380" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/177379" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/177381" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/177382" .

